BulkUpdateFeeCapsTest
├── When caller is not Fee Manager
│   └── It should revert with "NFM"
└── When caller is Fee Manager
    ├── When pools array and fee caps array are not the same length
    │   └── It should revert with "LMM"
    └── When pools array and fee caps array are the same length
        ├── When one of the pools is invalid
        │   └── It should revert
        └── When all pools are valid
            ├── When one of the fee cap is 0
            │   └── It should revert with "FC0"
            ├── When one of the fee cap is bigger than max fee cap
            │   └── It should revert with "MFC"
            └── When all the fee caps are within range
                ├── It should update the fee cap for all the pools
                └── It should emit a {FeeCapSet} event for all the pools